  GRAPH narr:Tx_20260424T120000Z {
    narr:Narrative_GoalDirectedPrimitive skos:note "perspective + goal + termination criteria + escalation criteria = a bounded autonomous agent. This unifies coding-agent back-pressure and interpersonal delegation. Extended 2026-04-24 as the Scarce-Expert Filter with Goal-Gated Escalation: an expert with scarce time currently serves as the answer-of-last-resort for repeated questions. Their perspective absorbs repeatable questions and gates escalation to the expert on a forward to a goal URL (booking form, referral form, office hours, DM, meeting). an early prospect's three use cases and the the customer's chief architect/the enterprise customer ARB use case all fit this same structural pattern. One instrument, variable escalation targets by deployment context." .
  }
}
